data.description: BUY OF 2023!!!   TONS of AFTER-PURCHASE ADDITIONS!  POPULAR LOCATION NEAR LAKE!  NICE QUIET NEIGBORHOOD!  LARGE FENCED YARD!  BEST ONE-LEVEL FLOOR PLAN!  2-CAR ATTACHED GARAGE + up to 4-CAR DETACHED GARAGE!  WONDERFUL SCHOOL AREA!  GREAT PRICE for ALL!!!  This upgraded home after purchase was FURTHER UPGRADED and made into a one-of-a-kind "special place."  Approximately $90,000 worth of visible/useable add-ons include:  huge 30'x26' high-ceiling garage/workshop, sunroom addition (by Patio Enclosures), Alexis Dual Massage walk-in shower/tub, backyard privacy fencing, upgraded lighting fixtures, Master Bedroom flooring, Vivint Alarm System (owned per seller, but with $38/month service fee).  There were also upgraded features prior to closing including:   Luxury vinyl plank flooring, R-30 insulation, low VOC carpet and paint, CFL bulbs, programmable thermostat, granite countertops, cherry-stained cabinetry, and more.   The ONE-LEVEL home is the most adaptable for all ages/demographics.  This beautiful home main living area uniquely opens to the Formal Dining area on one side while another side is totally open to Breakfast Room/Kitchen area.   This ONE-OF-A-KIND BUY is located in the popular area of Boiling Springs, with LAKE BOWEN nearby for the "lake people" and being only approximately 35 minutes to the major Woodruff Road shopping in GREENVILLE, only 20 minutes to SPARTANBURG, only 25 minutes to the GREENVILLE/SPARTANBURG INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT, 30 minutes to NC border and 60 minutes to the renowned mountainous city of ASHEVILLE!  So, this is an AMAZING LOCATION with access to I-85 and I-26 to take you into all the major cities of SC, plus the MOUNTAINS and NC cities/towns also!  The COMMUNITY of "Adens Place" gives its residents "room to breathe" with its 1/2-AC+ lots plus a very low yearly HOA fee!  These seller/owners went a step-above and cleared their entire lot so there would be plenty of room for pets and children to run and play.  When installing the privacy fence there, sellers put a gate for vehicle entry to the large, detached garage, if so needed.  This GARAGE could potentially park 4-cars (tandem) or could be used for a WONDERFUL WORKSHOP or MAN-CAVE...so many possibilities!!!  The current owners have invested so much extra $$$ into this home and would love to take it with them, but they cannot of course!   LUCKY BUYER to get this "BUY OF 2023"!!  HURRY TO BE THE BUYER of this FABULOUS PACKAGE/PLACE!!! (If SF is important to buyer, buyer must verify.)
